        "content": "| Method | API | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| GET | `/health` | Gateway health |\n| GET | `/metrics` | JSON gateway metrics |\n| GET | `/metrics/prometheus` | Prometheus metrics |\n| GET | `/api/riders` | List riders |\n| POST | `/api/riders` | Create rider |\n| GET | `/api/riders/{id}` | Get rider |\n| PUT | `/api/riders/{id}` | Update rider |\n| GET | `/api/riders/{id}/trips/report` | Rider trip report |\n| GET | `/api/drivers` | List drivers |\n| POST | `/api/drivers` | Create driver |\n| GET | `/api/drivers/{id}` | Get driver |\n| PUT | `/api/drivers/{id}` | Update driver |\n| PATCH | `/api/drivers/{id}/status` | Update driver status |\n| GET | `/api/drivers/{id}/trips/report` | Driver trip report |\n| POST | `/api/trips` | Create trip |\n| GET | `/api/trips/{id}` | Get trip |\n| POST | `/api/trips/{id}/accept` | Accept trip |\n| POST | `/api/trips/{id}/start` | Start trip |\n| POST | `/api/trips/{id}/cancel` | Cancel trip |\n| POST | `/api/trips/{id}/complete` | Complete trip |\n| GET | `/api/payments` | List payments |\n| GET | `/api/payments/{id}` | Get payment |\n| GET | `/api/trips/{id}/ratings` | List trip ratings |\n| POST | `/api/trips/{id}/rating` | Submit trip rating |\n| GET | `/api/ratings/{targetType}/{targetId}/summary` | Rating summary |",
